Class ParallelMultistartMultivariateOptimizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.math3.optim.BaseOptimizer<PAIR>
      • org.apache.commons.math3.optim.BaseMultivariateOptimizer<org.apache.commons.math3.optim.PointValuePair>
        • fastmath.optim.ParallelMultistartMultivariateOptimizer

  • public class ParallelMultistartMultivariateOptimizer
extends org.apache.commons.math3.optim.BaseMultivariateOptimizer<org.apache.commons.math3.optim.PointValuePair>
    Multi-start optimizer. This class wraps an optimizer in order to use it several times in turn with different starting points (trying to avoid being trapped in a local extremum when looking for a global one).
